task.summary: All Room CRUD functionality is fully functional
Each individual room now contains its own separate, distinct chat functionality.

Users are now able to create private rooms with one invited guest, then re-edit the room to add more individuals with private access. The general "room list" now correctly displays all public rooms, all rooms that were created by the user, and all private rooms that the user has invitations to.
CSS3 styling has been expanded and CSS3 animations have been incorporated into lists.
